homme (nom) [+concret] (W [+animé] (W [+humain] [+huII1aiI1]
la (pronom) [iconcret] U [ianimé] U [ihumain] []
je (PTOIIOIII) [+concret] n [+animé] n [+humain] [+hUII1aiI1]
